<li id="cite_note-82"><b><a href="#cite_ref-82" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFDean">Dean, Margaret. <a href="http://www.faeriechronicles.com" class="external text" title="http://www.faeriechronicles.com" rel="nofollow">"The Faerie Chronicles"</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.faeriechronicles.com" class="external free" title="http://www.faeriechronicles.com" rel="nofollow">http://www.faeriechronicles.com</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-02-19</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=The+Faerie+Chronicles&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Dean&amp;rft.aufirst=Margaret&amp;rft.au=Dean%2C+Margaret&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.faeriechronicles.com&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Fairy"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
